rebel in the rye is a 2017 american biographical drama film directed and written by danny strong . it is based on the book j. d. salinger : a life by kenneth slawenski , about the life of young writer j. d. salinger during world war ii . the film stars nicholas hoult , zoey deutch , kevin spacey , sarah paulson , brian d'arcy james , victor garber , hope davis , and lucy boynton . the film had its world premiere at the sundance film festival on january 24 , 2017 . it is scheduled to be released on september 15 , 2017 , by ifc films .